I have stored `/DEV/APP/CLIENT/KEYSTORE/PASSWORD`  and `/DEV/APP/CLIENT/TRUSTSTORE/PASSWORD` in SSM Param Store, with secure strings as value.

I am retrieving them in Lambda function as:

